						               													<description>You are eligible to inherit a vast fortune, which is hidden in the rooms of an abandoned mansion, and you only have one night to do it. There is one other little problem&amp;ndash;the mansion is haunted.&amp;#10;You will arrive at the mansion as night falls. The clock marks off the hours as you explore the decaying rooms and dark halls in search of the fortune. But you aren&amp;rsquo;t the only creatures that walk those floors. Monsters haunt the rooms of the mansion and intend to make you one of them.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If the monsters wound you three times, you will become one of the walking dead who hunt the live players, for by wounding them you can be restored to life. The living player who has collected the most money by sunrise will be declared the winner.&amp;#10;Yet the mansion holds another secret. Somewhere in the dust-covered rooms are six pages of scripture verses that can end the mansion&amp;rsquo;s curse and bring the dead players back to life. If you can find the six verses and give them all to one player before sunrise, the curse will end and all of my money will be distributed to the players equally.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The choice is yours: work together to assemble the verses before sunrise and share the victory, or work alone to avoid the monsters and dead players and try to collect the most money for yourself!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
